name: Manawa
overview: We’re a talented, fun and diverse IT consultancy with a single-minded focus to create awesome customer experiences for small and medium sized businesses. What we do best is look after you and own your problems so you can focus on what you do best. That means really listening, speaking to you straight and making you feel comfortable just the way you want. We provide IT support that takes the pain away and leaves you smiling every time. Passion to do right for customers drives us to make every experience fun, easy and affordable. We believe servicing your IT needs is something you really ought to enjoy.
